        that now enhance my approach to UX/UI and problem-solving.
        I am a disciplined team player who thrives on continuous learning
        and is actively seeking a Frontend or Full Stack internship or
        Junior position starting Summer 2026. I am fully open to relocation
        to contribute to impactful products and grow within a professional international team.
        </p>
